    "Our choice covers models that are regarded as flagship, regional models (Asian, European, Middle Eastern, and North American) in the size range of 7-13 billion parameters.",
    "Specifically, we use the following LLMs: Llama-2-13b-chat-hf (Touvron et al. 2023), Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.2 (Jiang et al. 2023), Starling-LM-7B-beta (Zhu et al. 2023), Qwen1.5-14B-Chat (Bai et al. 2023), Sailor-7B-Chat (Dou et al. 2024), Zephyr-7b-beta (Tunstall et al. 2023), and Falcon-7b-instruct (Almazrouei et al. 2023).",
    "foot_0 All models are considered significant through their widespread use and high leaderboard performance at the time of writing in late March 2024.",
